<title>USA: CBT Systems names Buckley as CEO.</title>
<headline>CBT Systems names Buckley as CEO.</headline>
<dateline>MENLO PARK, Calif 1996-12-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>CBT Systems Ltd said it named James Buckley as its new chief executive officer.</p>
<p>Buckley will report to William McCabe, who will retain the position of chairman of the board, effective immediately.</p>
<p>Buckley, 46, joined CBT Systems as president and chief operating officer in September 1996 after an 11-year career at Apple Computer Inc, where he served in various capacities, including senior vice president and president of Apple Americas, a sales and marketing organization.</p>
<p>Buckley will retain his title as president at CBT Systems in his new role.</p>
